MNEMO3=oval fetch merge employ repeat poverty combine dinosaur wise lucky example symbol orphan tragic figure taxi raccoon repeat journey again solar grape course valley

# Faucet drip amounts (per /credit call). Cooldown=0 so e2e tests can drip
